puzzlesolver.side

Class SimpleSide

  • java.lang.Object
    • puzzlesolver.side.SimpleSide
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Side>, Side

    public final class SimpleSide
extends java.lang.Object
implements Side
    An implementation of Side, where each side is represented by a list of Points. The coordinates of the Points are on an axis relative to the side. The x-axis is the line between the two endpoints of the side, and the y-axis is perpendicular to that, going away from the center of the piece.
